videos.description: Michigan State quarterback Brian Lewerke is picked off in the red zone by Sean Bunting, stalling the Spartans' first quarter drive.
videos.headline: Central Michigan picks off Michigan State in red zone

videos.description: Michigan State quarterback Brian Lewerke keeps the ball, bursts to the edge and walks in a 3-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Spartans take lead with rushing TD

videos.description: Central Michigan quarterback Tommy Lazzaro commits his second turnover of the game and is picked off by Michigan State defensive back Justin Layne.
videos.headline: Central Michigan QB misfires on Int

videos.description: Spartans running back Connor Heyward sheds a tackle and somersaults into the end zone for a 2-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Michigan State RB somersaults for TD

videos.description: Michigan State running back La'Darius Jefferson pounds into the end zone for a 2-yard touchdown, his first of his collegiate career.
videos.headline: Spartans RB bulldozes into end zone

videos.description: Central Michigan wide receiver Julian Hicks creates space on the slant route and snags a 10-yard touchdown pass from Tommy Lazzaro.
videos.headline: Central Michigan WR snatches 10-yard TD

videos.description: Central Michigan gets creative as wide receiver Jonathan Ward collects the lateral and rainbows a 29-yard touchdown pass to a wide open Tony Poljan.
videos.headline: Chippewas dig into their bag of tricks with 29-yard TD
